snippet.title: NES Longplay [344] Dick Tracy
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by JagOfTroy

Yet another video game based off of a comic series that made its first debut back in 1931.
The game has decent gameplay but the difficulty is quite troublesome due to how fast the enemies start attacking you once you appear on the screen. As most folks probably already know, you only have one life to get through each case and very few first aid kits found throughout the levels. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
